5600000000001, "text": " And how do you feel now?"}, {"start": 782.5600000000001, "end": 783.5600000000001, "text": " I feel embarrassed."}, {"start": 783.5600000000001, "end": 784.5600000000001, "text": " Pretty good, motherfucker."}, {"start": 784.5600000000001, "end": 785.5600000000001, "text": " Roll die."}, {"start": 785.5600000000001, "end": 788.5600000000001, "text": " Are you like famous or something?"}, {"start": 788.5600000000001, "end": 793.5600000000001, "text": " Yeah, I have 2,563 followers."}, {"start": 793.5600000000001, "end": 794.5600000000001, "text": " Is that funny?"}, {"start": 794.5600000000001, "end": 795.5600000000001, "text": " How many do you have?"}, {"start": 795.5600000000001, "end": 796.5600000000001, "text": " A thousand something."}, {"start": 796.5600000000001, "end": 797.5600000000001, "text": " Okay, so I have double you."}, {"start": 797.5600000000001, "end": 798.5600000000001, "text": " So why are you talking shit?"}, {"start": 798.5600000000001, "end": 801.5600000000001, "text": " Well, like, just what are you doing?"}, {"start": 801.5600000000001, "end": 804.5600000000001, "text": " I just watched the ass whooping in there."}, {"start": 804.5600000000001, "end": 805.5600000000001, "text": " All right, chat."}, {"start": 805.5600000000001, "end": 808.5600000000001, "text": " That concludes kind of this part of the video."}, {"start": 808.5600000000001, "end": 810.5600000000001, "text": " We're going to go back to the hotel, rest."}, {"start": 810.5600000000001, "end": 813.5600000000001, "text": " Well, I'm hitting the gym because I'm not lazy like Scotty."}, {"start": 813.5600000000001, "end": 814.5600000000001, "text": " I'm going to go get a pump in."}, {"start": 814.5600000000001, "end": 817.5600000000001, "text": " If you want to see behind the scenes content like that, add me on Snapchat."}, {"start": 817.5600000000001, "end": 818.5600000000001, "text": " I'm popping it up."}, {"start": 818.5600000000001, "end": 819.5600000000001, "text": " I'm trying to grow the Snapchat."}, {"start": 819.5600000000001, "end": 821.5600000000001, "text": " So please, everyone, go add me."}, {"start": 821.5600000000001, "end": 824.5600000000001, "text": " I post every day what I'm doing, behind the scenes, all that good stuff."}, {"start": 824.5600000000001, "end": 825.5600000000001, "text": " But anyways, I'm going to the gym."}, {"start": 825.5600000000001, "end": 826.5600000000001, "text": " I think Donnie's going to the gym."}, {"start": 826.5600000000001, "end": 827.5600000000001, "text": " Scotty's going to sleep."}, {"start": 827.5600000000001, "end": 829.5600000000001, "text": " And then we're going to go back out."}]}